      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="*This design could be subject to change based on specific country requirements/ feedback received from interlock teams and can be reviewed holistically in R3S8 for changes needed.&#10;&#10;The Manage Withholding Tax Determination - Customer Data is a process to track how much tax should be withheld by customers based on different countries' tax policies. Withholding tax certificates should be received as supporting documents to receive tax credit. "/>
